data.description: Luxury living in Skye Canyon. This stunning 2 story 5 bedroom home by Lennar offers an impressive sq ft of living space, nestled w/ in the gated community. Be greeted by the grandeur of the open-concept layout, providing ample room for relaxation & privacy. The modern design & craftsmanship are evident throughout that seamlessly blends style & functionality. The gourmet kitchen, a culinary dream, boasting premium SS appliances, granite countertops, & an oversized island perfect for gatherings. Natural light pours through large windows, illuminating the spacious living areas, creating a warm & inviting ambiance. The master suite is a true retreat, w/ a luxurious en-suite bath, a soaking tub & a walk-in closet & its own washer and dryer. Upstairs boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, laundry room, & large loft w/ balcony w/ views of the Valley & beautiful strip. The oversized backyard has a large built-in patio, turf, & pavers.
